content.rendered:
The Rustique Bar Stool is a beautifully designed vintage stool. It is crafted from wood and upholstered in a genuine leather.

The Rustique is perfect for bars, pubs, night clubs, hotels and other commercial venues alike.

The Rustique comes with a black wooden frame and a choice of leather colours.

For indoor use only.
